{"tid":1792244,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤：誠哥派錢算唔算洗黑錢","createTime":"2019-12-21T13:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T14:24:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23e2573233db83e2499a7c6d37d35e4b078a52e3","tid":1792244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191221/20828925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191221%2F20828925&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3C9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=8a6ca4d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191221%2F20828925&h=9a8f50a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191221/20828925</a><br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤：誠哥派錢算唔算洗黑錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576849615_a472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576849615_a472.jpg&h=bbfb0f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿澤以李嘉誠派錢，寸警方以「洗黑錢」拘捕星火同盟三男一女。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n警方前日在警總高調見傳媒，稱支援被捕抗爭者的星火同盟牽涉「洗黑錢」活動，拘捕三男一女，凍結7,000萬資金，引起全城譁然。杜汶澤昨日在facebook開火：「法律常識題，誠哥派錢，三唔識七，收錢嗰個算唔算洗黑錢？真心想知&hellip;&hellip;」特首林鄭月娥丈夫林兆波在前晚澳門回歸晚會，當全場拍手大合唱《歌唱祖國》，他卻面無表情，阿澤也在fb嘲道：「究竟林兆波係咪自己人？好難講！冇錯，佢的確冇拍手冇唱歌，但另一方面，佢好可能係『全香港X林鄭X得最少嘅人』嚟喎！咁呢條數又點計先？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576849614_23af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576849614_23af.jpg&h=b5c9b33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秋生嘲諷警方沒有自省能力，指記者並非拍警方執法，而是有否違法。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576849615_c4e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576849615_c4e8.jpg&h=2ef3c3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火同盟在今次反送中運動中，多次支援抗爭者。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n秋生嘲警冇自省能力<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，不平則鳴的黃秋生前日亦貼了一幅蒙面警的真實對話新聞，該蒙面警訓示傳媒話：「係咪記者朋友呀？影示威者啦，七個月喇，仲影警察執法。警察一定執法㗎啦！」秋生就在fb回應這位警察：「點解需要監察，點解需要獨立調查？佢講出咗個重點，就係七個月啦，佢都仲未明白人哋做乜影住佢，毫無自省能力。唔係影你執法，係影你有冇違法呀小朋友。」不少網民都留言支持秋生：「重點佢哋唔明，唔係阻止佢，係監察緊佢！」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n陳偉霆去澳門江蘇衛視跨年騷"},{"pid":"9dc1a4a28afc5d65ff79389956f4ce25faf249c7","tid":1792244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">聲援維吾爾族人權集會</span><br />\n12.22 星期日 <br />\n時間 : 15:30<br />\n地點 : 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span><br />\n學生歷量<br />\n公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Pk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FPk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3C9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=d01474fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Pk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw</a>"},{"pid":"11bcaabd42a33d53dea4a8cc750366bcb416cf46","tid":1792244,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"聽日有行動幫手推！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5Mi7yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5Mi7yZ.jpg&h=cc26222d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJYhDFF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJYhDFF.jpg&h=6b898915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［主線任務］聽日1530嘅維吾爾族集會獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"504e7afb17d77f10c1d603b90adfb14193aada28","tid":1792244,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited